      <title>苹果首席执行官蒂姆库克将于周五与特朗普会面</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-ceo-tim-cook-meet-with-trump-friday-2024-12-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士向路透社透露，苹果首席执行官蒂姆·库克将于周五晚在美国当选总统位于佛罗里达州的海湖庄园与唐纳德·特朗普会面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-ceo-tim-cook-meet-with-trump-friday-2024-12-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 23:24:23 GMT</pubDate>
