      <title>美国银行和高盛将向特朗普就职委员会捐赠未确定数额</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/bank-america-says-it-will-donate-undecided-sum-trumps-inaugural-committee-2024-12-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行与摩根大通公司是特朗普 2017 年就职典礼的最大两家银行捐助者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/bank-america-says-it-will-donate-undecided-sum-trumps-inaugural-committee-2024-12-13/</guid>
