      <title>古普塔 (Gupta) 获准推迟披露长期拖延的托克 (Trafigura) 案的文件</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gupta-granted-delay-document-disclosure-long-running-trafigura-case-2024-12-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[被大宗商品交易公司托克集团 (Trafigura) 指控犯有欺诈罪的普拉蒂克古普塔 (Prateek Gupta) 周五获得延期至 2 月底披露与这起旷日持久的案件相关的文件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gupta-granted-delay-document-disclosure-long-running-trafigura-case-2024-12-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 15:51:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
